                        SUSE Security Announcement

        Package:                evolution
        Announcement ID:        SUSE-SA:2008:014
        Date:                   Fri, 14 Mar 2008 10:00:00 +0000
        Affected Products:      SUSE LINUX 10.1
                                openSUSE 10.2
